{
  "stem": "19921.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 86.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There are still three medals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The big medal which is here, I didn't have it on that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because I retrieve-- as I mentioned to you, this medal was retrieved in 1994 through the Polish Council here in New York City.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In any event, three medals are there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There is a taped history, short history, which you-- when you pick up the receiver, it's-- you know, I-- my voice comes through there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it will be there for the past three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And also, the same exhibit, miniature exhibit was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not the uniforms as-- until-- just miniature and picture exhibit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Was displayed at the Intrepid Museum in New York City from March, 1995-- March, 1995 till September, 1995.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was a great success there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- Yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was liberate-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was interviewed by the BBC on the-- in 1994.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the exhibit-- I mean, the-- the show opened up in Britain in January.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it opened up throughout Europe, including Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- it was broadcasting by the BBC.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Britain, it was broadcast on Channel 4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a very lengthy interview, the way we doing now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Except there is only about three or four minutes there because there is about 16 or 18 different soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Fortunately, I was only the only one from the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is two-- were two Russian generals which are also interviewed, and they occupied Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the description there, the show opens up, actually, with my segment of liberating Majdanek, because that was the first ever extermination or concentration camp liberated.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was the first ever, was Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, Sobibor didn't count because there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the reason they opened up that show.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
